spec_data.Name: python-gdata
spec_data.Description:
This is a Python module for accessing online Google services such as:
- Base
- Blogger
- Calendar
- Health
- Picasa Web Albums
- Spreadsheets
- Documents List
- Contacts
- YouTube
- Google Apps Provisioning
- Code Search
- Notebook
- Webmaster Tools API
- Google Analytics Data Export API
- Google Book Search Data API
- Google Finance Portfolio Data API
- Google Maps Data API
- Sites Data API
- Issue Tracker Data API
